{
  "texts": [
    "Researchers must consider the protection of not only the primary user but also any third parties mentioned in posts.",
    "Several mitigation strategies are necessary.",
    "Rigorously stripping identifiable information during data collection is a primary step (8).",
    "Implementing secure data storage and access control policies is also important.",
    "Instead of reporting individual-level findings or using direct quotes, researchers can use aggregated data analysis or paraphrase sensitive content (16)."
  ]
}